<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulrich Pöllinger, Richter zu Altdorf</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Freilassung des Konrad Wiemer, da er kein Bürger zu Salzburg, sondern Nürnberg ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
