<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_306_r1l2"><expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Pöllıng<ex>er</ex></expan> Richter </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l3">cʒu Altdorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_306_r1l4"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Rıchter Als vvir nehſt <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> vvymer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener cʒu euch geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Ludwigen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l6">Grubers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Burgers wegen . den Jr gefangen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l7">habt ın dem namen als Er einer von <expan>Salcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l8">als vns fürbraht iſt . Alſo <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_306_r1l9"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> noch ledig laſſen wöllet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
