<ab><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Pölling<ex>er</ex></expan>, richter czu Altdorff</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her richter, als wir nehst
                                <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Wymer,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, czu euch gesant
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Ludwigen Grubers
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers wegen, den ir gefangen habt
                        in dem namen, als er einer von <expan>Salczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> sey, als
                        uns fürbraht ist. Also <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> noch ledig lassen wöllet
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das wollen etc.</ab>
